node.text: Making a perfect beef trifle isn't the only way to entertain your guests at home. Post a pic from the last get-together you had with your friends using #FriendsWeek for a chance to win the official Friends cookbook and a Friendsgiving entertaining guide! node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Friends on July 28, 2021. May be an image of 9 people and text that says 'F.R.I.E.N.D.S Week FRIENDSgiving DINNER pick only 1 from each row! who are you sitting next to? the moist maker what are you eating? rachel's monica's english mac trifle cheese classic roast turkey who did you bring with you? HBoMax wednesday july 28th'.

node.text: "You gotta have turkey on Thanksgiving. Thanksgiving with no turkey is like Fourth of July with no apple pie, or Friday with no two pizzas." - Joey Tribbiani
